\pard\qc\b\fs40\cf2 Introduction: The Billionaire Landscape\par\par
\pard\ql\b0\fs24\cf1
\bullet The global billionaire population is constantly shifting, influenced by market fluctuations, technological advancements, and geopolitical events.\par
\bullet This presentation focuses on the top 10 wealthiest individuals as of late 2024, based on estimates from reputable sources like Forbes and Bloomberg.\par
\bullet Wealth is primarily calculated based on the value of their holdings in publicly traded companies, private assets, and other investments.\par
\bullet It's important to note that these figures are estimates and can change rapidly.\par
