\bullet Technological innovation continues to be a primary driver of wealth creation.\par
\bullet Philanthropy plays an increasingly important role in how these individuals are perceived and the impact they have on society.\par
\bullet Understanding the sources and uses of this concentrated wealth provides valuable insights into the global economy and its future.\par
